## 0. Development Flow Overview

### 2-Agent Structure

| Agent | Role | Primary Responsibilities |
|-------|------|------------------------|
| **Cursor** | PM (Project Manager) | Task management, review, production deployment decisions |
| **Claude Code** | Worker | Implementation, testing, CI fixes, staging deployment |

### Workflow

```
Cursor (PM)          Claude Code (Worker)
    |                       |
    |  1. Task request      |
    |  (/handoff-to-claude)      |
    |---------------------->|
    |                       |
    |                       | 2. Assess status -> Implement -> Commit
    |                       |    (/sync-status -> /work)
    |                       |
    |  3. Completion report |
    |  (/handoff-to-cursor) |
    |<----------------------|
    |                       |
    | 4. Review & prod decision |
    |  (/review-cc-work)    |
    |                       |
```

