## 2. Role Assignments

### Cursor (PM) Responsibilities

- [ ] Define tasks and add to Plans.md
- [ ] Assign work to Claude Code
- [ ] Review completion reports
- [ ] Decide on and execute production deployment

### Claude Code (Worker) Responsibilities

- [ ] Implement tasks
- [ ] Run tests
- [ ] Commit & push
- [ ] Fix CI failures (up to 3 attempts)
- [ ] Staging deployment (when applicable)
- [ ] Create completion reports

